CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 25, 2006

[Cite as 04/25/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-2033.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2005-1047. State v. Upshaw.

Clark App. No. 05CA35. This cause is pending before the court on the certification of a conflict by the Court of Appeals for Clark County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for a warrant of removal to attend oral argument,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion is denied.
